author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
We check out two awesome 3D printed models of the Golden Gate Bridge--one a highly detailed replica of its iconic tower, and the other a 6-foot long model of the entire span of the bridge! The model kit comes courtesy of David Yun (aka day3Dlab), and it's an absolute joy to assemble. Thanks David for your kind words and this lovely kit!

6-foot scale model kit of Golden Gate Bridge: https://www.etsy.com/listing/975165664/golden-gate-bridge-model-replica-6-foot
Golden Gate Bridge tower model: https://makerworld.com/en/models/392123-golden-gate-bridge-tower-san-francisco-1-400#profileId-293177

Shot and edited by Norman Chan
Music by Jinglepunks
